arts.ttl: Empoli against Parma in the battle for survival
arts.sum: Parma have drawn six of their last eight League matches (W1 L1), as many draws as they recorded in the previous 22 games played in the competition (W4 L12). Empoli have drawn their last three home matches against Parma in Serie A; for the Toscani this is their longest current drawing streak against a single side in the competition on home soil (three also vs Fiorentina).
